prefuse.data.util

Class TableIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • prefuse.util.collections.AbstractLiteralIterator
      • prefuse.util.collections.IntIterator
        • prefuse.data.util.TableIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator, LiteralIterator

    public class TableIterator
extends IntIterator
    An iterator over table rows, providing convenience methods for accessing and manipulating table data.

    jeffrey heer
